<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='8503:8526'>　聶崇義曰連衣裳婦人服特圖此者明斬衰至緦麻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='8526:8534'>　婦人服皆然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='8534:8557'>　案殤小功布衰宜有圖因布衰之制略同於大功故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='8557:8571'>　不復圖而圖婦人衰裳於此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='8571:8598'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0051', 'WYG', '030-23a' );" name="030-23a" class="pb">[030-23a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
